The '''Intergalactic Droid Agency''' was an organization that specialized in placing dislocated or [[Manumission/Legends|manumitted]] [[Droid/Legends|droids]] during the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]]. They then put them in possession of companies and individuals where they would find their best use.

